* Carnage laied on the ground and looked up at the sky, she sighed as she 
turned her head and looked over at Cyber Claw...*

" Yes, it's over. You can come out now."

* She growled as she soon sat up and rested her elbows on her knees, it felt 
good to fight again but she had forgotten just how much power a charge had 
behind it.
Carnage then slowly stood up and looked over at the Ark, she had heard a 
female voice say that it was time to come back in and repair...it would be 
wise now to listen.
She steadied her stance...*

" Beast Mode!"

*Carnage transformed and began to make her way towards the base, she 
gestured to Cyber Claw to follow...*

" Come on, time to your act."
